room_title: Escape room "The Game Room" by Houdini's Room Escape in Cincinnati
room_description: Houdini himself has invited you over to his home! Little did you know, he was going to lock you in his parlor. But don’t get upset…he is only having a bit of fun with you, and he will let you out if you don’t let yourself out in 60 minutes. Besides, the trick is on him, because you will be the one having fun as you look for clues amongst the items in Houdini’s gaming parlor.
